  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is just a student project for fun, that have an idea simple as straight road to space. In spirit of endless runner genre.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose one of the four cyberpunk style environments (Cyber City top and down, Road to Moon, Mars Desert) and just drive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The project Inspired by synthwave videos on YouTube where music playlist accompanied by 80s style car, which drive through infinite Cyber space.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you wish you have a chance to put your songs to in game radio.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every CyberPunk style game have its own Cyber Bugs. Beware...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542380/extras/5fbfc136aa33328613f75cc8b5953bd2.poster.avif?t=1766092276\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542380/extras/5fbfc136aa33328613f75cc8b5953bd2.webm?t=1766092276\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542380/extras/5fbfc136aa33328613f75cc8b5953bd2.mp4?t=1766092276\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542380/extras/105ea56e72cb0e3f7332f60b69da9408.poster.avif?t=1766092276\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542380/extras/105ea56e72cb0e3f7332f60b69da9408.webm?t=1766092276\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542380/extras/105ea56e72cb0e3f7332f60b69da9408.mp4?t=1766092276\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is just a student project for fun, that have an idea simple as straight road to space. In spirit of endless runner genre.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose one of the four cyberpunk style environments (Cyber City top and down, Road to Moon, Mars Desert) and just drive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The project Inspired by synthwave videos on YouTube where music playlist accompanied by 80s style car, which drive through infinite Cyber space.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you wish you have a chance to put your songs to in game radio.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every CyberPunk style game have its own Cyber Bugs. Beware...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542380/extras/5fbfc136aa33328613f75cc8b5953bd2.poster.avif?t=1766092276\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542380/extras/5fbfc136aa33328613f75cc8b5953bd2.webm?t=1766092276\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542380/extras/5fbfc136aa33328613f75cc8b5953bd2.mp4?t=1766092276\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542380/extras/105ea56e72cb0e3f7332f60b69da9408.poster.avif?t=1766092276\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542380/extras/105ea56e72cb0e3f7332f60b69da9408.webm?t=1766092276\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542380/extras/105ea56e72cb0e3f7332f60b69da9408.mp4?t=1766092276\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
